# Purpose: Exclude local environments, caches, and machine-specific files from version control.
# Design: Keep project source, tests, docs, and data paths visible while ignoring generated clutter.
# Workflow: Git reads these patterns before staging files and skips matching local artifacts.
#
# Michael Garcia
# michael@mandedesign.studio
